HEADWORD: Sustained
<hw>Sus*tained"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Held up to a
certain pitch, degree, or level; uniform; <as>as, <ex>sustained</ex>
pasion; a <ex>sustained</ex> style of writing; a <ex>sustained</ex> note
in music</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

